      <title>炎热天气下野火包围加拿大油砂城</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/wildfires-encircle-canada-s-oil-sands-city-amid-hot-dry-weather</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大非官方油砂之都麦克默里堡周围爆发了一圈森林火灾，给世界第三大石油储备地的原油生产带来了新的威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/wildfires-encircle-canada-s-oil-sands-city-amid-hot-dry-weather</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 15:42:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>塞尔维亚最高法院撤销对力拓锂项目的禁令</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/serbia-s-top-court-rules-against-rio-tinto-s-lithium-project-ban</link>
      <description><![CDATA[塞尔维亚宪法法院推翻了一项政府法令，该法令在政治争议和环保人士的抗议中于 2022 年突然阻止了力拓集团在该国价值 24 亿美元的锂项目。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/serbia-s-top-court-rules-against-rio-tinto-s-lithium-project-ban</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 14:46:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特斯拉疯狂上涨引发估值现实考验</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/tesla-s-11-day-winning-run-prompts-a-valuation-reality-check</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特斯拉公司股价的强劲上涨在周四遭遇挫折，原因是有报道称该公司可能会推迟许多投资者寄予厚望的一项重要事件。然而，甚至在那之前，为多头辩护的难度就已经越来越大。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/tesla-s-11-day-winning-run-prompts-a-valuation-reality-check</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 12:12:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>参议院权衡拜登 FDIC 总裁人选 银行面临老对手</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/banks-face-old-foe-as-senate-weighs-biden-s-pick-to-run-fdic</link>
      <description><![CDATA[作为2008年金融危机后美国政府银行救助计划的最高监督者，克里斯蒂·戈德史密斯·罗梅罗对实施欺诈或滥用公共资金的银行家采取了强硬立场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/banks-face-old-foe-as-senate-weighs-biden-s-pick-to-run-fdic</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新兴市场货币受美国 CPI 数据推动创 5 月以来新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/emerging-market-stocks-hit-2-year-high-amid-global-rate-cut-bets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受美国 6 月份消费者价格意外下跌影响，新兴市场货币跃升至 5 月份以来的最高水平，巩固了人们对美联储将很快降息的预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/emerging-market-stocks-hit-2-year-high-amid-global-rate-cut-bets</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 09:06:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
